Subject: Web resources are not available on macOS Sequoia
Description: Hello, Customer name is PrivatBank. They reported, that after install EPP client 3.0.3.1 to the new version of macOS Sequoia, some web resources like speedtest.net.ua and docs.google started to be unavailable. I will attach all screenshots and logs. We suggested to the customer to enable the Intercept VPN feature to test if it will help.
